sub_title: Honours Student, BSc International Business Administration at Rotterdam School of Management, Erasmus University
summary:
Having been brought up in multiple countries with parents originating from different continents, I thrive in international environments.
The varied environments that I have always been in touch with have enabled me to quickly sense people in order to adapt and be considered an effective leader.
My discipline and perseverance have brought me where I am today and I consider being nowhere near what I can achieve yet in the business world.
I have no boundaries but currently focus on a future in entrepreneurship and or marketing, with sustainability as a must.
By achieving what I want, I hope I can transmit my smile to as many people as possible and make the world a better place.
